        "content": "<p>What isn’t clear about the error message? The angle bracket notation denote a constructor application, and the expected type is not an inductive type but a forall.</p>",
        "id": 508029515,
        "sender_full_name": "Patrick Massot",
        "timestamp": 1742910992
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>So the argument to <code>Or.inr</code> should start with <code>fun a : G ↦ </code></p>",
