        "sender_full_name": "Patrick Massot",
        "timestamp": 1742911023
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It’s probably clearer to replace that last line by </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">left</span>\n<span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span>\n<span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 508029754,
        "sender_full_name": "Patrick Massot",
        "timestamp": 1742911048
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Then you need to browse the file around <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Monoid.exponent#doc\">docs#Monoid.exponent</a> to find a relevant lemma in order to prove <code>a^2 = 1</code>.</p>",
